{"word":"G5486 - χάρισμα - chárisma - khar'-is-mah - Gift","slug":"G5486","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χάρισμα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>chárisma"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khar'-is-mah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Gift"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C7;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x03C3;&#x03BC;&#x03B1; - charisma</b> - <i>char'-is-mah</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G5483\">G5483</a>; a (divine) <i>gratuity</i>, that is, <i>deliverance</i> (from danger or passion); (specifically) a (spiritual) <i>endowment</i>, that is, (subjectively) religious <i>qualification</i>, or (objectively) miraculous <i>faculty:</i> - (free) gift."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2168\">G2168</a>, <a href=\"#/G2169\">G2169</a>, <a href=\"#/G2170\">G2170</a>, <a href=\"#/G4796\">G4796</a>, <a href=\"#/G5463\">G5463</a>, <a href=\"#/G5479\">G5479</a>, <a href=\"#/G5483\">G5483</a>, <a href=\"#/G5484\">G5484</a>, <a href=\"#/G5485\">G5485</a>, <a href=\"#/G5487\">G5487</a>, <a href=\"#/G884\">G884</a>"}]}